cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper presents a new dataset for evaluating visual odometry algorithms using both stereo and plenoptic cameras. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of state-of-the-art algorithms, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the dataset was recorded in challenging scenarios, suggesting a potential interest in graphics (cs.GR) for visualization purposes.
